Zest/grate orange peel (no white; 1 teaspoon). Peel oranges and cut into segments; squeeze membranes (or other orange) for juice (1/2 cup). Cut fennel in half lengthwise; slice fennel, white part only (2 cups). Combine all ingredients (except spring mix and almonds) in salad bowl. Add spring mix and toss to coat evenly; top with almonds and serve.